<blockquote>Q. So you fired something like sixty-seven shots?<br> A. Right.<br> Q. And you killed how many? At that time?<br> A. Well, I fired them automatic, so you can’t- You just spray the area on them and so you can’t know how many you killed ‘cause they were going fast. So I might have killed ten or fifteen of them.<br> Q. Men, women, and children?<br> A. Men, women, and children.<br> Q. And babies?<br> A. And babies.</blockquote>
