<p><a href="#sdfootnote27anc" name="sdfootnote27sym">27</a>The question that has to be left aside in this essay, yet which remains troubling and worth exploring, is what does it mean to choose as one’s first and last name the same word, a proper name doubled, and divide the two by an initial.</p>
